    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Buffalo</placeName>
                <date>Nov. 21st 1854</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>
                <hi rend="indent(1)">
                    <placeName>Phild.</placeName>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <p>According to a letter from <date>Sept. 1st</date> I<lb/> have <sic>Recd</sic> the
                Books &amp; thought to sell<lb/> some of them but till now <sic>i</sic> was not<lb/>
                looking to sell any for you, as most the<lb/> People thinks they got high Price on
                it<lb/> nevertheless <sic>i</sic> will try <sic>agin</sic> what <sic>i</sic> can
                to<lb/> &amp; if <sic>i</sic> should not succeed in selling them<lb/>
                <sic>i</sic> wish you would direct me what <sic>i</sic><lb/> shall do with them.</p>
            <p><sic>in</sic> the over said letter is <sic>mentiond</sic><lb/> Freight paid,
                    <sic>i</sic> had to pay 50 Cents<lb/> by Express <sic>i</sic>
                <del>showd</del> showed them the letter &amp;<lb/> they answers me the
                    <sic>fraight</sic> was only<lb/> paid to <placeName>N. Y.</placeName> &amp; not
                farther.</p>
            <p>&amp; also <sic>i</sic> was requested of <persName>Mr. H. Cohne</persName><lb/> here
                as he does not wish for the Occident<lb/> &amp; he <sic>dit</sic> not order
                    <sic>anny</sic>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Yours very respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">E. J. Bernheimer</persName>
                <placeName>57 Elliot St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>An</p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>N371 Walnut St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>
                    <hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi>
                </placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
